2023-05-11 cage

	* src/text.lisp:

	- changed event binding for callback in "make-text-tag-button":
	previously  the function  bound to  the parameter  "over-callback" was
	bound  to the  event "Enter",  but  now has  been bound  to the  event
	"Motion".

